<div class=3D"mw-heading mw-heading2"><h2 id=3D"nobel_Nobel_Laureates"><cod=
e>nobel</code> Nobel Laureates</h2></div>
  <p>We continue practicing simple SQL queries on a single table.</p>
  <p>This tutorial is concerned with a table of Nobel prize winners:
  </p>
  <pre style=3D"width:20em;">nobel(yr, subject, winner)</pre>
<p>Using the <code>SELECT</code> statement.</p>
<div class=3D"mw-heading mw-heading2"><span class=3D"id">1. </span><h2 id=
=3D"Winners_from_1950">Winners from 1950</h2></div>
<div class=3D"qu zood" data-qnumber=3D"1" data-qid=3D"1">
<p>Change the query shown so that it displays Nobel prizes for 1950.=20
</p>
<div class=3D"def mw-highlight mw-highlight-lang-sql mw-content-ltr" dir=3D=
"ltr"><pre><span></span><span class=3D"k">SELECT</span><span class=3D"w"> <=
/span><span class=3D"n">yr</span><span class=3D"p">,</span><span class=3D"w=
"> </span><span class=3D"n">subject</span><span class=3D"p">,</span><span c=
lass=3D"w"> </span><span class=3D"n">winner</span>
<span class=3D"w">  </span><span class=3D"k">FROM</span><span class=3D"w"> =
</span><span class=3D"n">nobel</span>
<span class=3D"w"> </span><span class=3D"k">WHERE</span><span class=3D"w"> =
</span><span class=3D"n">yr</span><span class=3D"w"> </span><span class=3D"=
o">=3D</span><span class=3D"w"> </span><span class=3D"mi">1960</span>
</pre></div><div name=3D"frm__1" id=3D"frm__1" class=3D"frm"><span class=3D=
"quf"><textarea spellcheck=3D"false" rows=3D"6" cols=3D"47" class=3D"sql" i=
d=3D"txtar_1">SELECT yr, subject, winner
  FROM nobel
 WHERE yr =3D 1960
</textarea><button class=3D"submitSQL">Submit SQL</button><button class=3D"=
reset">restore default</button></span></div><div class=3D"res">result</div>
<div class=3D"ans mw-highlight mw-highlight-lang-sql mw-content-ltr" dir=3D=
"ltr"><pre><span></span><span class=3D"k">SELECT</span><span class=3D"w"> <=
/span><span class=3D"n">yr</span><span class=3D"p">,</span><span class=3D"w=
"> </span><span class=3D"n">subject</span><span class=3D"p">,</span><span c=
lass=3D"w"> </span><span class=3D"n">winner</span>
<span class=3D"w">  </span><span class=3D"k">FROM</span><span class=3D"w"> =
</span><span class=3D"n">nobel</span>
<span class=3D"w"> </span><span class=3D"k">WHERE</span><span class=3D"w"> =
</span><span class=3D"n">yr</span><span class=3D"w"> </span><span class=3D"=
