</pre></div>
</div>
<div class=3D"mw-heading mw-heading2"><span class=3D"id">2. </span><h2 id=
=3D"1962_Literature">1962 Literature</h2></div>
<div class=3D"qu zood" data-qnumber=3D"2" data-qid=3D"2">
<p>Show who won the 1962 prize for literature.=20
</p>
<div class=3D"def mw-highlight mw-highlight-lang-sql mw-content-ltr" dir=3D=
